S.FORM: Dennis Bell nalecuhan i Cincinnati, Ohio, nanu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, pahanhanan tu kawaw ayza. Dennis Bell i 1973 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 5 ku uwac atu silsil 83, namapili' tu nu New York Knicks putiput. 6 bulad 2 demiad, 1951 a mihca, Dennis Bell, miunduay. namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players
